description:
Establishment of a Dynamic Market pursuant to section 34 of the Procurement Act 2023 for the physical supply of gas & electricity to all Authority sites along with associated invoicing and query management services. A Dynamic Market is a procurement mechanism that:
•remains open to new suppliers throughout its duration;
•allows suppliers to apply for admission at any time;
•enables the Authority to conduct competitive selection processes among admitted suppliers

Establishment of a Dynamic Market pursuant to section 34 of the Procurement Act 2023 for the physical supply of electricity to all Authority sites along with associated invoicing and query management services. 
A Dynamic Market is a procurement mechanism that:
•remains open to new suppliers throughout its duration;
•allows suppliers to apply for admission at any time;
•enables the Authority to conduct competitive selection processes among admitted suppliers

Translation and interpretation providers to provide translation services for those whose first language is BSL in the provision of:
•	Face to Face interpreting for interviews, meetings, consultation and social care requirements;
•	Video interpreting (i.e. video conference)
